  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🚀 WF-OPS-BOOKING-FULFILLMENT-v1\n**Motor B2B de Fulfillment — ATLAS OPS**\n\n### FASE OUTBOUND (Solicitud al mayorista)\n```\nTRIGGER (cada 5 min) → Query bookings\n→ JOIN leads + marketing_offers\n→ Mapear email proveedor\n→ Gemini redacta correo B2B\n→ Gmail Send\n→ UPDATE bookings (email_sent)\n```\n\n### FASE INBOUND (Confirmación del mayorista)\n```\nTRIGGER (cada 10 min) → Gmail poll\n→ Filtrar respuestas pendientes\n→ Gemini extrae localizador\n→ UPDATE bookings (provider_locator)\n→ POST → Antigravity Squad (WhatsApp)\n```\n\n### MATRIZ DE PROVEEDORES:\n- `soltravel` → soltravel06@gmail.com\n- `deseo` → deseoreservas@gniall.com.do ⚠️ verificar\n- `opera` → ventas8@operahotel.com.do\n- `sunparadise` → sunreservas@sunparadise.com.do\n- `tierraverde` → reservas@mitierraverde.com\n\n### COLUMNAS NUEVAS en bookings:\n`fulfillment_status`, `provider_name`, `provider_email`,\n`pax_details`, `children_ages`, `provider_locator`,\n`gmail_thread_id`, `outbound_sent_at`\n\n⚠️ **POST-IMPORT**: Configurar credencial Gmail en\nnodos 03_GMAIL_SEND y 09_GMAIL_POLL",
        "height": 620,
        "width": 500,
        "color": 3
      },
